Shanghai B-shares close slightly lower in volatile trade 
Shanghai B-shares closed slightly lower Thursday in volatile trade with
shares dropping from intra-session highs after rebounding off initial
lows, dealers said.
The Shanghai B-share index inched down 0.02 points to close at 137.2 on
turnover of 88.88 million dollars.
The A-share index gained 12.19 points or 0.8 percent to 1,518.83 on
turnover of 11.34 billion yuan (1.37 billion dollars).
